text: residential area which is kept so clean .. u would love here to walk, cycle and drive

Located just next to Simei Green Line MRT. Many continental food options can get here, bit rush can be seen here at peak hours.
Indian, local, Thai, Chinese, Indo foods can get easily here, both side of the building we have a food stalls and at both side you can have beers as well, rates are moderate, withing $7-8 you can get almost all items.
Bread shop, fruits, clinic, grocery stores are available. Smoking zone is also available.
always confused about the sign boards and layout at the basement. relatively empty when i went to the food court to get lunch.
